{
  "description": "A close-up, top-down view of a collection of smooth, rounded rocks and pebbles of varying sizes and colors. The rocks range from light beige and tan to shades of gray, brown, and reddish-brown. Some rocks exhibit subtle banding or patterns. Scattered among the rocks are a few strands of dry, golden-brown grass or straw. The lighting is bright and appears to be natural sunlight, casting slight shadows that enhance the texture and three-dimensionality of the rocks. The composition is dense and fills the entire frame.",
